# ğŸ¤ Voice-to-Text Note App (Go + React + Deepgram)

A lightweight full-stack app that lets users **record voice notes**, **preview them**, and **transcribe them into text** using Deepgram AI. Built with Go (backend) and React (frontend), this project is fast, efficient, and perfect for voice journaling, note-taking, and more.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- ğŸ™ï¸ Record audio directly from browser  
- ğŸšï¸ Select microphone input  
- ğŸ§ Preview recordings before transcribing  
- â³ Transcribe later option (manual trigger)  
- ğŸ§  Real-time transcription via Deepgram  
- ğŸ—ƒï¸ Stores last 3 recordings in memory (frontend)  
- ğŸ’¾ Saves transcripts in SQLite (backend)  
- âš™ï¸ Simple REST API (Go-based)  
- ğŸŒ CORS-enabled for local dev  

